'''Allen Iverson''' ([[7 Kamena]], [[1975]] - ), umukinnyi wamamaye cyane muri shampiyona ya [[basketball]] yo muri [[Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika]], biravugwa ko kuri ubu yaba ari kugana mu bukene bukabije nyuma y’aho aviriye muri [[NBA]] akajya gukina muri [[Turukiya]] mu ikipe [[Beşiktaş]].

Amakuru dukesha Philadelphia Inquirer aratumenyesha ko n’ubwo Iverson kuri ubu ari muri iyo kipe Besiktas, ntibiyibuza gutsindwa umusubizo, mu gihe ubwo yasinyishwaga contrat yo kuyikinamo, yaba abayobozi, abafana cyangwa abakinnyi bayikinamo, bose bari biruhukije bumva ko babonye Mesiya.

